Context: George Brown College values employer partnerships and seeks to build productive communities with businesses nationally and internationally. They welcome interested parties to contact them for potential collaborations and partnerships. There are several ways to get involved with the college, including reaching out to include your company on their videos page, signing up to receive application deadlines and college news, or contacting them via email at alumni@georgebrown.ca or asking.george@georgebrown.ca. The college's phone number is 416-415-2000 with a TTY number of 1-877-515-5559. Their social media hub can be visited through the website. They advocate for inclusion, diversity, and social responsibility. It is important to verify George Brown College fee requirements as the information on their website is subject to change without notice.
